Fabry, Kearns-Sayre, etc)","guid":"5yF-upgnwQNY6N6fENNonA","children":[]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"61","text":"- Adquiridos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"- Idiopática (enfermedad de Lev, enfermedad de Lenegre)","guid":"kQgCY-XcjiW0gaSo7KMEdw","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"- Isquemia/infarto (generalmente infero-posterior)","guid":"x0LPHzGO28OxhnZ2Id29Bw","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"65","text":"- Cirugía valvular aórtica o mitral","guid":"1JU8vvueDmrFzd1aJ7vhIA","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"65","text":"- Fármacos (betabloqueadores, calcioantagonistas, antiarritmicos, digoxina)","guid":"8vmA9qEis8ugFseSbkb0gw","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"65","text":"- Enfermedades infiltrativas,\\Ninflamatorias o infecciosas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"- Sarcoidosis, amiloidosis, hemocromatosis","guid":"u2lW1QGFGIJuiB_8oN8nKA","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"70","text":"- Miocarditis (viral, autoinmune, fiebre reumática)","guid":"s12HVrad8cEhre9tR73h6w","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"70","text":"- Endocarditis con absceso para-valvular aórtico","guid":"1vfRxD4khTwMpcTMuukFBQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"74","parent":"65","text":"- Trastornos neuromusculares (ataxia de Friedreich, distrofia miotónica)","guid":"c4aSiHHEaOeubYcDUcQe7Q","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"65","text":"- Enfermedades neurodegenerativas (Parkinson, Alzheimer)","guid":"db6nkVO003LzWEj9IsL_wQ","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"65","text":"- Radioterapia mediastínica","guid":"HBO5uG0LShi3vr-ojwJmzA","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"65","text":"- Otros: Estenosis aórtica calcificada, mixoma auricular, hipervagotonía, postablación septal","guid":"y4YsQ8br3VvDKBFnAEZa4A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"28","text":"- Otras","guid":"g2UolBjzCu2dyjXQeNHl6Q","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"- Hiperpotasemia severa (> 7 mEq/L)","guid":"lqjlE80F6XMnF-TchK9GDw","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"78","text":"- Hipotermia moderada-severa (< 30°C)","guid":"qel6m8UXo_eyrXklVWEvFw","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"78","text":"- Intoxicación por fármacos o drogas (betabloqueadores, calcioantagonistas,\\Nantiarrítmicos, clonidina, opioides, organofosforados, etc)","guid":"SPonngH-ujRIJ7cjhnwYsg","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"78","text":"- Hipotiroidismo severo (coma mixedematoso)","guid":"kM0s6Bkr9UPbdiczNv5DZg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"83","parent":"0","text":"Fármacos\\Ncronotrópicos\\Nnegativos","guid":"PS_VVEZR7aLreI60jFBO9w","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"- Betabloqueadores\\N(BB) (3)","guid":"ioAqdhH6vqK-B2MyWWLsIQ","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"- Propranolol, atenolol, metoprolol, carvedilol, etc.","guid":"I-jdXrYbdjXm2RoZFYDHfQ","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"84","text":"- Mecanismo: Bloqueo receptores β1 → ↓ FC y ↓ contractilidad","guid":"Pj3GoK6q0Uv5Cs5aVfX3JQ","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"84","text":"- Usos: HTA, ICC, arritmias, cardiopatía isquémica","guid":"pNs9mmdD4c78MXpxBNng3Q","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"84","text":"- Precaución en PM con bradiarritmias preexistentes o hipotensión","guid":"DvXPBI1xEVRMnqjpZDr0fQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"83","text":"- Bloqueadores canales de calcio no\\Ndihidropiridínicos (BCC-ND) (4)","guid":"Y1wEfor-MQKYYF9ISTbCug","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"- Diltiazem, verapamilo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"89","text":"- Mecanismo: Bloqueo canales Ca tipo L → ↓ FC, ↓ contractilidad y ↓ conducción AV","guid":"nIFoqkloPmGO7ZuNOISabg","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"89","text":"- Usos: HTA, arritmias supraventriculares, cardiopatía isquémica","guid":"x1LXGfaBSEpuk54MTMPbFQ","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"89","text":"- Mayor riesgo de bradicardia y BAV en PM","guid":"qCPkYD1tnRdAsO1c1AVZSQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"94","parent":"83","text":"- Antiarrítmicos (AA) (5)","guid":"68XOW4_r8ifLbtaTS_6IBw","children":[{"id":"