odo sinusal y trastornos de conducción","guid":"C62K0-7a_Kw7-UJh1-EwKA","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"110","text":"- Polifarmacia → Mayor riesgo de efectos adversos e interacciones","guid":"MnkXwidfpvhwKcYrQP45TA","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"110","text":"- ↓ Función renal y hepática → Alteración farmacocinética y acumulación","guid":"mhTrn08J1MH1_4HSPKfQqA","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"110","text":"- ↓ Mecanismos de compensación cardiovascular → Mayor impacto hemodinámico","guid":"obyghA4MEpPkXePnQA7M7g","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"110","text":"- Presentación atípica (mareo inespecífico, caídas, delirium)","guid":"Z9MViAKFY62Sizysw6XChg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"116","parent":"0","text":"Clínica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"117","parent":"116","text":"- Antecedentes:","guid":"H75OhYVu56EI-ucQbQxCTg","children":[{"id":"118","parent":"117","text":"- Uso de fármacos cronotrópicos negativos","guid":"ECkIKwap-L4HD1eVrmMByA","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"117","text":"- Cardiopatía estructural","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"117","text":"- Hipotiroidismo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"121","parent":"116","text":"- Cuadro clínico:","guid":"5XDKTNd0s2KbkBa7bPhHhQ","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"- Asintomática o\\Nfatiga crónica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"121","text":"- Presíncope y síncope\\Nsi FC muy baja","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"121","text":"- Palpitaciones por\\Nextrasístoles o escape\\Nventricular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"121","text":"- Signos de bajo gasto\\N(hipotensión, mala perfusión)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"126","parent":"116","text":"- Factores de mal\\Npronóstico:","guid":"Cn5foTbTTLY2-gIKCE6xOg","children":[{"id":"127","parent":"126","text":"- Síncope o presíncope (OR 3.5 para eventos) (7)","guid":"wVLpz4tHAQDrdPsq6FEoyg","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"126","text":"- QRS ancho (bloqueo avanzado)","guid":"elMuN_iebq5e8Yv6E4-_aw","children":[]}]},{"id":"129","parent":"116","text":"- Complicaciones:","guid":"5_tr8EudX7iPM1f2w9jyZA","children":[{"id":"130","parent":"129","text":"- Taquiarritmias auriculares por hiperautomatismo\\N(fibrilación/aleteo auricular)","guid":"9nGOuxX2WIEyzEQpB-EuoQ","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"129","text":"- Taquicardia ventricular si ritmo de escape anómalo","guid":"FiUYXC1tUCOyhhmtMMRMkw","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"129","text":"- Síncope, insuficiencia cardíaca","guid":"oiPWBc_p7C-Gf4rekkefsA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"133","parent":"0","text":"Estudio:","guid":"3CWdIG-4pJDR-v75FWCpmQ","children":[{"id":"134","parent":"133","text":"- ECG 12\\Nderivaciones:","guid":"_B3YKoes-kU-31Gu6R_wfQ","children":[{"id":"135","parent":"134","text":"- Identificar ritmo bradicárdico y\\Ntipo (sinusal vs bloqueo)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"134","text":"- Bloqueo AV 2do grado Mobitz II o\\Navanzado sugiere necesidad de\\Nmarcapasos (S 70%, E 98%) (8)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"137","parent":"133","text":"- Holter si bradicardia intermitente","guid":"FOfUO6Gx-wiNAQFgZ4FdeQ","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"133","text":"- Pruebas autonómicas si se sospecha disfunción sinusal extrínseca","guid":"sJmjTLyklNXoVVQhVhj2zg","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"133","text":"- PEF si sospecha de BAV paroxístico con síncope","guid":"3omwDp3ttQhr3BpMeh-gRg","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"133","text":"- Laboratorio:","guid":"_cAi5qNBpczqTqW57Q6EiQ","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"- Hemograma (descartar anemia)","guid":"-ByDrTRGLFsXxUqgjy__Tw","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"140","text":"- Electrolitos (descartar hiper K)","guid":"LzPgb5POz0kbsU_ihduzBQ","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"140","text":"- TSH (descartar hipotiroidismo)","guid":"Y7UvV4VZhMU8ZDtBwLztZw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"144","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"145","parent":"144","text":"- Bradicardia sinusal: FC<60 con ritmo sinusal","guid":"aOeTTrLlUKVm9F5TvKIrGw","children":[{"id":"146","parent":"145","text":"- Variante: Paro o pausa sinusal (ausencia ondas P ≥ 3 seg)","guid":"o4Ta0sDKZNBKYufWv84qJQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"147","parent":"144","text":"- Bloqueos AV:","guid":"Qq43PVoFflF989vo4eh_iw","children":[{"id":"148","parent":"147","text":"- 1er grado: PR >200 ms con conducción 1:1","guid":"CxlIKSMTWWuGNibinIAwqg","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"147","text":"- 2do grado: Conducción\\NAV intermitente","guid":"Lgs08Ovh7at1AikjE89vgA","children":[{"id":"150","parent":"149","text":"- Mobitz I (Wenckebach): Alargamiento progresivo PR hasta bloqueo","guid":"QkPSHrhvGzeIzYhmYw_y4Q","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"149","text":"- Mobitz II: Bloqueo súbito sin alargamiento previo","guid":"JYu46EJnmiALvf_M8mqsrQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"152","parent":"147","text":"- 3er grado (completo): Disociación AV completa","guid":"wSm41mCaOOCTohuopfWfhw","children":[]}]},{"id":"153","parent":"144","text":"- Gold standard diagnóstico: ECG 12 derivaciones","guid":"momvoF7X8y65RCWY_i557w","children":[{"id":"154","parent":"153","text":"- Sensibilidad ECG para detectar bradicardia: 80-90% (9)","guid":"YAqjqJz6mq_VvGOgyy0JNg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"155","parent":"0","text":"Diagnósticos\\Ndiferenciales:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"156","parent":"155","text":"- Ritmos de escape auriculares, de la unión o ventriculares por ritmo sinusal enfermo","guid":"Bf0TkBdKkcpkDEUlVgAKug","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"155","text":"- Bloqueo sinoauricular vs pausa/paro sinusal","guid":"3LcfDC3JDhCsvu8kzD5gSA","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"155","text":"- Flutter auricular con conducción AV lenta","guid":"Mbpo852aQHvNn-fFTJNIlQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"159","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"- Objetivo: Tratar causa subyacente, aliviar síntomas y prevenir complicaciones","guid":"bUCtxW3bO2srL42cHkFJEg","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"159","text":"- No farmacológico:","guid":"B3ahXJPIATRxy2UHn1czmA","children":[{"id":"162","parent":"161","text":"- Suspender o ajustar fármacos cronotrópicos negativos si es posible","guid":"RlLlXNEQdNNtKZXQfdezIw","children":[]}]},{"id":"163","parent":"159","text":"- Farmacológico:","guid":"fUiJlB2Oq5x4KHKDRqcKdg","children":[{"id":"164","parent":"163","text":"- 1era línea: Atropina 0.5-1 mg IV, repetir hasta 3 mg. Uso transitorio (cuidado glaucoma)","guid":"tnmnWoJkn0Rig2DFuKbbnQ","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"163","text":"- 2da línea: Isoproterenol (Isuprel) infusión 2-10 ug/min si atropina inefectiva","guid":"8caXVz8yxVOEaQ6m9tc6xQ","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"163","text":"- 3era línea: Dopamina o epinefrina infusión si no respuesta a lo anterior","guid":"r6RC9-VwSLSy8hoFjV8cjw","children":[]}]},{"id":"167","parent":"159","text":"- Marcapasos transitorio si inestabilidad a pesar de fármacos","guid":"MmlO9acokc1WxzsnS7NszQ","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"159","text":"- Marcapasos definitivo si bradicardia sintomática persistente o BAV avanzado/completo","guid":"gVFJH3udlcc6OeRoSPuMNw","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"159","text":"- Interacciones:","guid":"3wWst-VWG7-Lbvw49Pvm1g","children":[{"id":"170","parent":"169","text":"- Atropina puede precipitar glaucoma agudo en predispuestos","guid":"S9HT0A7CroMn6ByMpiGgGg","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"169","text":"- Isoproterenol y dopamina pueden causar taquicardia e isquemia","guid":"Pxjv3pmF_heeVP3Bgx58Bg","children":[]}]},{"id":"172","parent":"159","text":"- Conceptos\\Nfarmacológicos clave:","guid":"8EnAPFDkhWrimXPg2bT3AQ","children":[{"id":"173","parent":"172","text":"- Atropina: antimuscarínico, antagoniza efecto vagal (metabolismo hepático vía CYP450)","guid":"5s-sRmn7_8AwwMqx7DlWWA","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"172","text":"- Isoproterenol: betaagonista no selectivo, estimula receptores beta 1 y 2 (metabolismo COMT)","guid":"ewiH3SKzgbyN2a0PKfun9w","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"172","text":"- Dopamina: precursor NA con efecto dosis dependiente (dosis beta a dosis altas)","guid":"tzM7VNc83U2uCUd37bUhWw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"176","parent":"0","text":"Seguimiento y\\Npronóstico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"177","parent":"176","text":"- Seguimiento según\\Netiología y cuadro clínico","guid":"WV5QQFkUypiHmImx63pRwA","children":[{"id":"178","parent":"177","text":"- Bradicardia asintomática: ECG c/6-12 meses","guid":"in-lH9K0cY04J_B7m8X9Hg","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"177","text":"- Bradicardia sintomática o BAV avanzado: considerar marcapasos y seguimiento según especialista","guid":"tQZqOSwIy6nEVu2Uro3euw","children":[]}]},{"id":"180","parent":"176","text":"- Pronóstico: Variable según causa.\\NBuen pronóstico si causa reversible\\No con marcapasos.","guid":"Zved1tw-XnAgOW2jHqSiNQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"181","parent":"0","text":"Prevención:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"182","parent":"181","text":"- Identificar y tratar precozmente causas reversibles\\N(ej. hipotiroidismo, suspender fármacos)","guid":"cNi2P31G_rkegwTX8UiSXg","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"181","text":"- Considerar marcapasos profiláctico en pacientes con\\Ncardiopatía estructural y BAV 1er grado muy sintomático","guid":"rjSK8BfP6pdBW1H2AzuxyQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"184","parent":"0","text":"Tamizaje:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"185","parent":"184","text":"- No existe tamizaje poblacional","guid":"qwF9JIqVeFf8VQH7XKiU9A","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"184","text":"- ECG en pacientes con síncope, palpitaciones, o cardiopatía estructural (S 80%, E 90%) (9)","guid":"5kVUiazPN6hXPRO6rlwk7w","children":[]}]},{"id":"187","parent":"0","text":"Aspectos Geriátricos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"188","parent":"187","text":"- Mayor prevalencia de bradicardia en ancianos (deterioro nodo sinusal, fibrosis del sistema de conducción)","guid":"j7nAEnmLqDSFKkujZ0L2_w","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"187","text":"- Presentación atípica: Caídas, síncope, deterioro cognitivo","guid":"mQvfcuAQgASau6HekYDm1Q","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"187","text":"- Polifarmacia aumenta riesgo (betabloqueadores, diltiazem, digoxina, etc)","guid":"qxJVvETnUDKVovtoMgKHLA","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"187","text":"- Mayor riesgo de complicaciones (síncope con caídas, insuf. cardíaca)","guid":"QHKh74NMqWcx6rxpYuPdWw","children":[]}]},{"id":"192","parent":"0","text":"Referencias:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"193","parent":"192","text":"1. Kusumoto FM, et al. 2018 ACC/AHA/HRS Guideline on\\Nthe Evaluation and Management of Patients With\\NBradycardia and Cardiac Conduction Delay. J Am Coll\\NCardiol. 2019;74(7):932-987.","guid":"GHNr33kPb6JARMXtBd3HAA","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"192","text":"2. Mangrum JM, DiMarco JP. The evaluation\\Nand management of bradycardia. N Engl J\\NMed. 2000;342(10):703-9.","guid":"nrROr1pBUJYzFZkKuwkAmg","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"192","text":"3. Wenckebach K. Zur analyse des\\Nunregelmassigen pulses. Z Klin\\NMed. 1899;37:475–88.","guid":"Pq-JoAly6EgWS2DVi2OLdw","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"192","text":"4. Jensen PN, et al. Incidence of and risk factors for\\Nsick sinus syndrome in the general population. J Am\\NColl Cardiol. 2014;64(6):531-8.","guid":"-MlQjqPOFIybHD2W992TPg","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"192","text":"5. Cárdenas Ibarra L et al. Prevalencia de\\NSíndrome Bradicardico en una población\\Ngeriátrica de Santiago de Chile. Rev chil\\Ncardiol. 1988;7(1):13-17.","guid":"qPx6D8wxuwcbcv-LnWHwPQ","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"192","text":"6. Edhag O, Swahn A. Prognosis of patients with\\Ncomplete heart block or arrhythmic syncope. Acta\\NMed Scand. 1976; 200(6):457-63.","guid":"v5FUFf7Gd7N4P61ai0mbWA","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"192","text":"7. Alboni P, et al. Clinical spectrum of\\Nneurally mediated reflex syncopes.\\NEuropace. 2004;6(1):55-62.","guid":"JpuRyzRBhyW7ZU7eZRiYlQ","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"192","text":"8. Brignole M, et al. 2013 ESC Guidelines on cardiac\\Npacing and cardiac resynchronization therapy. Eur\\NHeart J. 2013;34(29):2281-329.","guid":"WQTTOdXlTXnm4HJaOSzdGA","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"192","text":"9. Kotwal S, Perera S. The Diagnostic\\NValue of Electrocardiography in Identifying\\NArrhythmic Causes of Syncope. Cardiol\\NRev. 2020;28(2):59-64.","guid":"ePauTfUSQvOIH5uwNn9FFA","children":[]}]},{"id":"202","parent":"0","text":"Abreviaturas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"203","parent":"202","text":"- AV:\\NAuriculoventricular","guid":"tkfx-xDfg-4q0DMQDEHRLw","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"202","text":"- BAV: Bloqueo\\Nauriculoventricular","guid":"Q5ldLAKx3jaJ09GC8ZQwrA","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"202","text":"- FC:\\NFrecuencia\\Ncardíaca","guid":"jWPv5vv11X4HchKP_WmsHQ","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"202","text":"- lpm: latidos\\Npor minuto","guid":"wSEzTiIpyd6bv32CwAKQyw","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"202","text":"- ms: milisegundos","guid":"J24jCoi-lsB9zSLL4RbmCA","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"202","text":"- OR: Odds ratio","guid":"MUikQ0lvyXwtSNLU6PgXLg","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"202","text":"- RR: Riesgo relativo","guid":"5zQB8I2xjvkpARxaFO0Hgw","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"202","text":"- S: Sensibilidad","guid":"iPamJGcxlmqTBU1dThQc0Q","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"202","text":"- E: Especificidad","guid":"9zVDNQmDt2nbnBodr-RHYg","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"202","text":"- PEF: Prueba de\\Nesfuerzo farmacológica","guid":"VvVwvat9SixFH5tWCZa7Rg","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":212,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Cardiología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Cardiología","filename":"Bradicardia-2024","id":"map_233","resolved_references":[]}